{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were signs, which were not good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those signs were probably increasing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a number of times that there were executions of hostages, or people who were arrested.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, indeed, in the-- in mid-July, those things were-- there were more signs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I came, there was an execution of over 100 people, 110 people I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them were Jewish police, which was just like that, without any reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was, again, they were taken by name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were executed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that must have been around maybe in the second half of July.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, suddenly, the atmosphere started getting very panicky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I came home from school, or from sitting in this garden, I think on the 19th of July, I saw a car, a Gestapo car, somewhere near [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found out that they were arresting all kinds of people, like doctors, and lawyers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father even had-- I think we were discussing if he should stay or hide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- and there were as well things, like in the house next door there was living a man who was a cousin, or a nephew, of the [INAUDIBLE] who was one of those ghetto barons, who had very close connections with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And his name was [INAUDIBLE] as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to some people he knew in our house that things are very bad, because there is a new unit which came to Warsaw, a German unit.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they called it, I think, [GERMAN], or something, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We just heard those words.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we, of course, didn't know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that, they are going to start some activity against the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
